    <div class="button-span">
        { ifDisplay.disabledButton && <button aria-disabled="true" type="button">This is a disabled button</button> }

        { ifDisplay.buttonVariationsAll ? ifDisplay.buttonVariations.map( variant => <button
            class={`button-${variant}`}
            set:text={`This is a ${variant} button`}
            type="button"
        /> ) : '' }
    </div>
) }

{ ifDisplay.buttons && ifDisplay.buttonTypes && <div class="button-span">
    <a class="button" href="#" target="_blank">This is a link with a <code>button</code> class</a>
    <button type="submit" set:text="This is a submit button" />
    <button type="reset" set:text="This is a reset button" />
</div> }

<slot name="three" />

<p>Cras neque arcu, fermentum non elementum ac, tincidunt ut nibh. Proin blandit, nisl at volutpat pulvinar, massa nisl vulputate risus, eget porttitor neque mi id augue.{ ifDisplay.textPage && ' Integer porttitor egestas facilisis. Quisque eget nibh hendrerit, ornare nisl sit amet, faucibus enim. Vivamus venenatis, libero et laoreet laoreet, purus dolor fringilla massa, sit amet luctus dolor ligula nec metus. Suspendisse ut justo vel nisi porta tincidunt.' }</p>

<Heading
    displayHeading={2 + displayHeading}
